<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA48">
<l>emakkiyām viṇṇāṭṭuk kuccamatām vīṭṭai</l>
<l>yamaittiruntō maḵtaṉṟē yāmā ṟamaippolinta</l>
<l>meṉṟōḷi kāraṇamā veṅkōṭṭē ṟēḻuṭaṉē</l>
<l>koṉṟāṉai yēmaṉattuk koṇṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For ourselves we have achieved liberation that is at the height</l>
<l>of the heavenly land – that, isn’t it, is the way it is – directing</l>
<l>[our] mind towards him who killed cruel-horned bulls, seven together,</l>
<l>for the sake of her with soft shoulder luxuriant [like] bamboo.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
